      <title>python装饰器学习</title>
      <link href="/2020/10/31/python%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0%E5%99%A8%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/"/>
      <url>/2020/10/31/python%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0%E5%99%A8%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; 苦于看不懂项目代码里的各种花里胡哨的装饰器，于是认真翻了一下廖雪峰博客里关于python装饰器一节的内容，总算是对装饰器有了一个大概的了解了。这里记录一下学习的过程吧</p><h1 id="1-python函数的特性"><a href="#1-python函数的特性" class="headerlink" title="1. python函数的特性"></a>1. python函数的特性</h1><p>&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; 在学习装饰器的原理之前，需要回顾python的函数所具有的一些特性：</p><ul><li>函数是一个对象，可以被赋值给其他变量</li><li>函数可以作为另一个函数的返回值</li><li>函数可以作为另一个函数的输入参数</li></ul><h1 id="1-1-函数可以被赋值给其他变量"><a href="#1-1-函数可以被赋值给其他变量" class="headerlink" title="1.1 函数可以被赋值给其他变量"></a>1.1 函数可以被赋值给其他变量</h1><p>&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; 在python中万物皆可是对象，函数也不例外。在下面的例子中，先定义了一个函数<code>today</code>，然后将其赋值给了一个变量<code>a</code>，然后我们便可以通过<code>a()</code>的方法来调用函数了。<br><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">today</span>():</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="string">&#x27;今天是2020年10月31日&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">a = today       <span class="comment"># 将函数today赋值给变量a</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; a()         <span class="comment"># 通过a来调用函数</span></span><br><span class="line">今天是<span class="number">2020</span>年<span class="number">10</span>月<span class="number">31</span>日</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h1 id="1-2-函数可以作为另一个函数的返回值"><a href="#1-2-函数可以作为另一个函数的返回值" class="headerlink" title="1.2 函数可以作为另一个函数的返回值"></a>1.2 函数可以作为另一个函数的返回值</h1><p>&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;  平时我们常用的函数，一般是返回一个数，或是一个list，string，dict等等。因为上面说到了函数本身也是一个对象，因此自然而然的，<strong>函数也可以被当做某个函数的返回结果来返回</strong>。下面的代码中，函数<code>return_a_function</code>的返回结果就是其内部定义的另一个函数<code>foo</code>，第一个括号的调用结果就是foo，而第二个括号调用就等价于执行语句<code>foo()</code>，最后的返回结果就是：”我是一个被返回的函数”。<br><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">return_a_function</span>():</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">foo</span>():</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="string">&#x27;我是一个被返回的函数&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> foo</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; return_a_function()</span><br><span class="line">&lt;function __main__.return_a_function. &lt; locals &gt; .foo() &gt;</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; return_a_function()()</span><br><span class="line">我是一个被返回的函数</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h1 id="1-3-函数可以作为另一个函数的输入参数"><a href="#1-3-函数可以作为另一个函数的输入参数" class="headerlink" title="1.3 函数可以作为另一个函数的输入参数"></a>1.3 函数可以作为另一个函数的输入参数</h1><p>&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; 函数也可以作为参数输入给另一个函数。下面的代码中，<code>ask_date</code>函数便接受一个函数作为入参，输出的时候，先会打印一句“今天是几号？”，然后再返回入参函数的调用结果。<br><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">today</span>():</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="string">&#x27;今天是2020年10月31日&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">ask_date</span>(<span class="params">func</span>):</span></span><br><span class="line">    print(<span class="string">&quot;今天是几号？&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> func()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; ask_date(today)</span><br><span class="line">今天是几号？</span><br><span class="line">今天是<span class="number">2020</span>年<span class="number">10</span>月<span class="number">31</span>日</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h1 id="2-装饰器"><a href="#2-装饰器" class="headerlink" title="2. 装饰器"></a>2. 装饰器</h1><p>&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; 什么是装饰器，一个最简单直观的理解方式是：<strong>装饰器也是一个函数，只不过它接收某一个函数作为参数，并返回另一个函数。</strong></p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">a_new_decorator</span>(<span class="params">a_func</span>):</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    a_new_decorator是一个装饰器函数，接收的参数a_func是一个函数，返回的结果wrapTheFunction也是一个函数</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    被这个装饰器装饰的函数，在原有功能的基础上，会在开头打印一句话，显示执行函数。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    __name__是函数对象固有的一个属性，可以以string格式返回该函数对象的函数名</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    &#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">wrapTheFunction</span>(<span class="params">*args, **kwargs</span>):</span></span><br><span class="line">        print(<span class="string">&quot;开始执行函数%s&quot;</span> % a_func.__name__)     <span class="comment"># 这行代码则是装饰器为目标函数新增的功能</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> a_func(*args, **kwargs)              <span class="comment"># 这行代码保证了装饰器不改变目标函数的原功能</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> wrapTheFunction</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; 比如上面的代码就定义了一个装饰器函数<code>a_new_decorator</code>，他接收的参数<code>a_func</code>是一个函数，同时返回的结果<code>wrapTheFunction</code>也是一个函数。那怎么使用这个装饰器呢？一个非常简单的语法糖用法如下：只要用<code>@</code>加上装饰器函数名，然后放在需要被装饰的函数的定义部分上方即可。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">@a_new_decorator</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">today</span>():</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="string">&#x27;今天是2020-10-31&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; today()</span><br><span class="line">开始执行函数today</span><br><span class="line">今天是<span class="number">2020</span><span class="number">-10</span><span class="number">-31</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; 装饰器的意义是：<strong>在不改变被装饰的函数的原有功能的前提下，额外增加新的功能。</strong>比如上面的代码，被装饰的函数<code>today</code>的原有功能是打印今天的日期，而在经过装饰器装饰过后，函数又额外打印了一句日志。用装饰器来为原函数动态添加新的功能是很方便的一件事，因为我们不用特意修改原函数内部的代码了。<strong>装饰器为原函数增加的新的功能，则是由装饰器函数所返回的那个函数决定的。</strong>在这个例子里，装饰器函数<code>a_new_decorator</code>返回的函数<code>wrapTheFunction</code>，其定义就是先输出一句日志，然后再调用被装饰的函数本体(a_func)。上面的语法糖写法，等价于下面的直观写法：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">today = a_new_decorator(today)</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; today()</span><br><span class="line">开始执行函数today</span><br><span class="line">今天是<span class="number">2020</span><span class="number">-10</span><span class="number">-31</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; 不过这种装饰器函数定义的方法，会将原目标函数的名字和docstring重写了。如果我们想要保留原目标函数的名字的话，只需要用python自带的一个wraps函数即可：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> functools <span class="keyword">import</span> wraps</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">a_new_decorator</span>(<span class="params">a_func</span>):</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 用wraps装饰器，并传入a_func为参数，即可保留目标函数的名字和docstring</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">    @wraps(a_func)</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">wrapTheFunction</span>(<span class="params">*args, **kwargs</span>):</span></span><br><span class="line">        print(<span class="string">&quot;开始执行函数%s&quot;</span> % a_func.__name__)     <span class="comment"># 这行代码则是装饰器为目标函数新增的功能</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> a_func(*args, **kwargs)              <span class="comment"># 这行代码保证了装饰器不改变目标函数的原功能</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> wrapTheFunction</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@a_new_decorator</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">today</span>():</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;输出今天的日期&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="string">&#x27;今天是2020-10-31&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; print(today.__name__)</span><br><span class="line">today</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; print(today.__doc__)</span><br><span class="line">输出今天的日期</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; 总结一下装饰器的要点：装饰器本身是一个函数，接收函数为参数，返回另一个函数。其中，<strong>返回的函数的定义里会有一行代码是执行接收的函数，这保证了装饰器不改变目标函数原有的功能。</strong>而其余的代码则是对原函数功能的扩充。</p><h1 id="3-带参数的装饰器"><a href="#3-带参数的装饰器" class="headerlink" title="3. 带参数的装饰器"></a>3. 带参数的装饰器</h1><p>&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; 有时候我们可能希望通过一些参数来控制装饰器所新增的功能的效果，这时候就需要编写一个含有参数的装饰器。<strong>其形式相当于是原本的装饰器函数外面再嵌套一层函数，并且这个函数显式的接受参数，也就是一个三层嵌套的函数</strong>。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">log</span>(<span class="params">text</span>):</span>  <span class="comment"># text参数会在@语法调用装饰器的时候显式指定，用以控制下面wrapTheFunction的效果。</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">a_new_decorator</span>(<span class="params">a_func</span>):</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 用wraps装饰器，并传入a_func为参数，即可保留目标函数的名字和docstring</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">        @wraps(a_func)</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">wrapTheFunction</span>(<span class="params">*args, **kwargs</span>):</span></span><br><span class="line">            print(<span class="string">&quot;开始执行函数%s&quot;</span> % a_func.__name__)     <span class="comment"># 这行代码则是装饰器为目标函数新增的功能</span></span><br><span class="line">            print(<span class="string">&quot;装饰器接收的参数是:&quot;</span>, text)</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> a_func(*args, **kwargs)              <span class="comment"># 这行代码保证了装饰器不改变目标函数的原功能</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> wrapTheFunction</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> a_new_decorator</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@log(text=&#x27;hahaha&#x27;)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">today</span>():</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;输出今天的日期&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="string">&#x27;今天是2020年10月31日&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; today()</span><br><span class="line">开始执行函数today</span><br><span class="line">装饰器接收的参数是: hahaha</span><br><span class="line">今天是<span class="number">2020</span>年<span class="number">10</span>月<span class="number">31</span>日</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; 对于带参数的装饰器，其调用原理和下面代码等价。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">today = log(text=<span class="string">&#x27;hahaha&#x27;</span>)(today)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; 具体地来说，首先执行<code>log(text=&#39;hahaha&#39;)</code>，返回的是<code>a_new_decorator</code>函数，然后再执行<code>a_new_decorator(today)</code>，最后返回<code>wrapTheFunction</code>函数。<strong>直观的来说，就是通过传入不同参数<code>text</code>的方式，来控制函数<code>log</code>所返回的装饰器其最终的效果不同。而要想达到这个目的，必定需要在最内层的函数中（即<code>wrapTheFunction</code>函数内部），用到最外层的输入参数。</strong></p>]]></content>
      
      
